'''歐洲冬青'''（[[學名|學名]]''Ilex aquifolium''）是一種原產於[[西歐|西歐]]及[[南歐|南歐]]、西北[[非洲|非洲]]及西南[[亞洲|亞洲]]的[[冬青|冬青]]。<ref name=fe>{{Cite web|author=Flora Europaea|url=http://rbg-web2.rbge.org.uk/cgi-bin/nph-readbtree.pl/feout?FAMILY_XREF=&GENUS_XREF=Ilex&SPECIES_XREF=aquifolium&TAXON_NAME_XREF=&RANK=|title=''Ilex aquifolium''|access-date=2010-07-01|archive-date=2012-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120216104637/http://rbg-web2.rbge.org.uk/cgi-bin/nph-readbtree.pl/feout?FAMILY_XREF=&GENUS_XREF=Ilex&SPECIES_XREF=aquifolium&TAXON_NAME_XREF=&RANK=|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=mc>{{Cite web|author=Med-Checklist|url=http://ww2.bgbm.org/mcl/PTaxonDetail.asp?NameId=1263&PTRefFK=1273|title=''Ilex aquifolium''|access-date=2010-07-01|archive-date=2017-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170814021453/http://ww2.bgbm.org/mcl/PTaxonDetail.asp?NameId=1263&PTRefFK=1273|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=rushforth>{{Cite book en|author=Rushforth, K.|year=1999|title=Trees of Britain and Europe|publisher=Collins|id=ISBN 0-00-220013-9}}</ref><ref name=fnwe>{{Cite web|author=Flora of NW Europe |url=http://ip30.eti.uva.nl/BIS/flora.php?selected=beschrijving&menuentry=soorten&id=3088 |title=''Ilex aquifolium'' |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090609025123/http://ip30.eti.uva.nl/BIS/flora.php?selected=beschrijving&menuentry=soorten&id=3088 |archivedate=2009-06-09 }}</ref>

歐洲冬青是常綠樹，高達10-25米，樹幹[[直徑|直徑]]40-80厘米闊，樹皮呈灰色及光滑。[[葉子|葉子]]長5-12厘米及闊2-6厘米，形狀各有不同。幼樹及低枝上的葉子每邊有3-5條尖刺，交替指向上下；在較高的樹枝上的葉子有很少或沒有尖刺。<ref name=rushforth/><ref name=fnwe/>

[[花朵|花朵]]是雌雄異株的，呈白色及有4瓣，由[[蜜蜂|蜜蜂]]傳播[[花粉|花粉]]。[[果實|果實]]呈紅色，直徑闊6-10毫米，有4個果核，一般在秋末成熟。果實因含有[[冬青素|冬青素]]而味道非常苦<ref name=Heinz1975>{{Cite book en|author=Heinz, A.|year=1975|title=Drogenkunde|publisher=W. de Gruyter|id=ISBN 313566001X}}</ref>，[[鳥類|鳥類]]故此很少會吃它們，直至到了[[冬天|冬天]]結霜後，它們較為軟身才變得可口。

==毒性==
歐洲冬青的提取物可以令[[老鼠|老鼠]]的[[血壓|血壓]]下降至致命水平。<ref>{{Cite journal en|author=Lasserre, B., Kaiser, R., Chanh, P. H., Ifansyah, N. and Gleye, J.|year=1983|title=Effects on rats of aqueous extracts of plants used in folk medicine as antihypertensive agents: ''Ribes nigrum'', ''Olea europaea'', ''Leonotis nepetaefolia'', ''Ilex aquifolium'', ''Viscum album'', ''Erigeron canadensis'', ''Solidago virga-aurea''|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_naturwissenschaften_1983-02_70_2/page/95|journal=Naturwissenschaften|volume=70|pages=95–6}}</ref>

[[冬青素|冬青素]]可以令[[人類|人類]]中毒，刺激[[胃部|胃部]]及[[小腸|小腸]]，並會對[[神經系統|神經系統]]及[[心臟|心臟]]有害。成年人食用20顆歐洲冬青就足以致命。<ref name=rushforth/><ref name=fnwe/>

==醫藥用途==
歐洲冬青很少在醫藥上被使用，但其可以利尿、減輕[[發燒|發燒]]的情況及有舒緩作用。<ref>{{Cite book en|author=Wren, R.C.|year=1988|title=Potter's New Cyclopedia of Botanical Drugs and Preparations|publisher=C.W. Daniel|id=ISBN 0-85207-197-3}}</ref>

歐洲冬青含有[[皂苷|皂苷]]、[[黃嘌呤|黃嘌呤]][[可可鹼|可可鹼]]及冬青黃質。<ref name=Heinz1975/>

